first install docker on your system

create new folder on your file system (e.g. eventbussenderdocker)

copy following files in this folder:
	Dockerfile	
	vertxeventbussender-1.0.0-SNAPSHOT-fat.jar

create the docker image:	docker build -t eventbussender .

start the docker container: docker run -v /inputfolderonyourfilesystem:/opt/input eventbussender

HAVE FUN!!!